description: While most chefs are used to working in a fully staffed kitchen, when you work as a personal chef, you become a one-man show. It can be challenging to shift from a team driven focus to solely accountable, but some enjoy the challenge. Below are some of the average and expected responsibilities as a personal chef, but these may differ based on your employer
cooking_method: A braised chicken has much, to recommend it right now. For one, it's easy.It spares you the brining and marinating that can make roasting a chore. It fills the house with delicious smells. A warm sauce that materializes, somewhat miraculously
